Jessica Chaffin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jessica_Chaffin 0 Jessica Chaffin is an American actress, comedian, and writer best known as part of the comedy duo Ronna and Beverly with Jamie Denbo. She is also known for her recurring role as Coco Wexler on Nickelodeon's Zoey 101 and appearing in the films Spy and The Heat. Chaffin starred as Marie Faldonado in the CBS sitcom Man With A Plan, opposite Matt LeBlanc.
